<div id="search-box">

  <div class="content">
    <h1 class="home-tagline">Hack your next stay...</h1>
    <h2 class="home-subheader">Search and book listings in your destination of choice</h2>

    <form class="form-search" action="/search" method="GET">
      <div class="input-group">
        <input type="text" name='query' class='form-control' id='searchinput input-large search-query' placeholder='Enter a neighborhood in San Francisco...'>
        <span class="input-group-btn">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-info">Search</button>
        </span>
      </div>
    </form>

  </div>
</div>
 

<div class="container">
  <div class="neighborhoods">
      <% @hoods.each do |hood, pic| %>
      
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
          <div class="thumbnails">
            <%= image_tag(pic, size: "328x250") %>
            <div class="caption">
              <h3><%= hood %></h3>
              <p><a href="#" class="btn btn-info" role="button">Book Tour</a> <a href="#" class="btn btn-default" role="button">Details</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      <% end %>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="hacker-friends">
</div>

<div class="community">
  <div class="content">
    <h2 class="title">Community Living</h1>
    <h3 class="subtitle">Together everyone shares more...</h3>
    <p class="blurb">Whether you're a free spirit looking to connect with other like-minded souls or a tech entrepreneur looking to meet other innovators and disruptors, community living just might be for you.  San Francisco presents us with a unique opportunity to live and share space with others looking to consciously raise themselves to the next level both on a spiritual, material and emotional plane.</p>
    <p class="blurb">As social creatures, while we might need some alone time, benefit greatly from a synergistically positive intentional space shared with others.  The collective energy and effort that can be combined with such an intentional purpose could be the boost you need! You don't have to struggle alone anymore, come join one of our houses and start living to your potential. </p>
  </div>
</div>

